'''欧盟全球人权制裁-{制}-度'''（{{lang-en|EU Global Human Rights Sanctions Regime}}）是[[欧盟|欧盟]]于2020年12月7日通过的一项机制，旨在惩罚对严重侵犯人权行为负责的非欧盟国家人员。受美国[[全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法|全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法]]的启发，该机制要求欧盟维护全球侵犯人员的名单，并对他们实施各种制裁，如[[签证|签证]]禁令和[[资产冻结|资产冻结]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=MEPs call for EU Magnitsky Act to impose sanctions on human rights abusers |url=https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20190307IPR30748/meps-call-for-eu-magnitsky-act-to-impose-sanctions-on-human-rights-abusers |website=The European Parliament |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2019-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191226010449/https://www.europarl.europa.eu/news/en/press-room/20190307IPR30748/meps-call-for-eu-magnitsky-act-to-impose-sanctions-on-human-rights-abusers |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 背景 ==
历史上，欧盟曾多次因侵犯人权对其他国家实施制裁，如1989年起因[[六四事件|六四事件]]对中国实施武器禁运，<ref>{{cite web |title=Specfic restrictive measures in relation to the events at the Tiananmen Square protests of 1989 |url=https://www.sanctionsmap.eu/api/v1/pdf/regime?id[]=10&lang=en |website=EU Sanctions Map |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705214623/https://www.sanctionsmap.eu/api/v1/pdf/regime?id%5B%5D=10&lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>冻结伊朗某些压制和折磨人权活动家官员的资产。<ref>{{cite web |title=Restrictive measures in relation to serious human rights violations in Iran |url=https://www.sanctionsmap.eu/api/v1/pdf/regime?id[]=17&id[]=18&lang=en |website=EU Sanctions Map |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705141929/https://www.sanctionsmap.eu/api/v1/pdf/regime?id%5B%5D=17&id%5B%5D=18&lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref>然而，这些制裁只是针对特定国家的个别制裁，这种对每个国家使用新制裁政策的方法有其局限性，如在欧盟议会通过立法程序需要时间和相关过程的政治影响。<ref>{{cite web |title=An EU human rights sanctions regime? |url=https://www.europarl.europa.eu/RegData/etudes/ATAG/2019/637892/EPRS_ATA(2019)637892_EN.pdf |website=The European Parliament |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200207144613/http://www.europarl.europa.eu/RegData/etudes/ATAG/2019/637892/EPRS_ATA%282019%29637892_EN.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2016年，美国颁布[[全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法|全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法]]，该法案允许美国政府在全球范围内对侵犯人权者实施制裁。<ref>{{cite web |title=The US Global Magnitsky Act |url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2017/09/13/us-global-magnitsky-act |website=Human Rights Watch |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2017-09-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170928171158/https://www.hrw.org/news/2017/09/13/us-global-magnitsky-act |dead-url=no }}</ref>欧盟的多个成员国很快效仿美国，通过类似法律打击国外侵犯人权行为；同年，[[爱沙尼亚|爱沙尼亚]]也通过法律禁止被认定侵犯人权的外国人入境，<ref>{{cite news |title=Estonia joins US in passing Magnitsky law |url=https://euobserver.com/foreign/136217 |accessdate=5 July 2020 |work=EU Observer |date=9 December 2016 |archive-date=2016-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210120235/https://euobserver.com/foreign/136217 |dead-url=no }}</ref>隨後立陶宛、<ref>{{cite news |last1=Picard |first1=Renee |title=Lithuania: Parliament Adopts Version of Magnitsky Act |url=https://www.occrp.org/en/daily/7265-lithuania-parliament-adopts-version-of-magnitsky-act |accessdate=5 July 2020 |work=Organized Crime and Corruption Reporting Project |date=16 November 2017 |archive-date=2018-07-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711145620/https://www.occrp.org/en/daily/7265-lithuania-parliament-adopts-version-of-magnitsky-act |dead-url=no }}</ref>拉脱维亚、<ref>{{cite news |last1=Carolan |first1=Sinead |title=Latvia Becomes Final Baltic State to Pass Magnitsky Law |url=https://www.occrp.org/en/daily/7621-latvia-becomes-final-baltic-state-to-pass-magnitsky-law |accessdate=5 July 2020 |work=Organized Crime and Corruption Reporting Project |date=9 February 2018 |archive-date=2019-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190719014327/https://www.occrp.org/en/daily/7621-latvia-becomes-final-baltic-state-to-pass-magnitsky-law |dead-url=no }}</ref>與当时还是成员国的[[英国|英国]]相继通过类似法律。<ref>{{cite news |title=UK House of Commons Passes the Magnitsky Asset Freezing Sanctions |url=https://www.occrp.org/en/daily/6104-uk-house-of-commons-passes-the-magnitsky-asset-freezing-sanctions |accessdate=5 July 2020 |work=Organized Crime and Corruption Reporting Project |date=21 February 2017 |archive-date=2017-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222120546/https://www.occrp.org/en/daily/6104-uk-house-of-commons-passes-the-magnitsky-asset-freezing-sanctions |dead-url=no }}</ref>荷兰议会也要求政府启动类似立法，但荷兰政府拒绝并认为这样的立法在欧盟层面会更加有效，这导致了欧盟层面对人权制裁机制的讨论。<ref>{{cite web |title=The Magnitsky Act Comes to the EU: A Human Rights Sanctions Regime Proposed by the Netherlands |url=https://www.nhc.nl/the-magnitsky-act-comes-to-the-eu-a-human-rights-sanctions-regime-proposed-by-the-netherlands/ |website=Netherlands Helsinki Committee |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200204003855/https://www.nhc.nl/the-magnitsky-act-comes-to-the-eu-a-human-rights-sanctions-regime-proposed-by-the-netherlands/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 发展 ==
2018年底，荷兰政府起草了一份名为《迈向欧盟全球人权制裁机制》的立场文件，并邀请其他成员国前往海牙进行讨论。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Jozwiak |first1=Rikard |title=Netherlands Proposes New EU Human Rights Sanctions Regime |url=https://www.rferl.org/a/netherlands-propose-new-eu-human-rights-sanctions-regime/29609488.html |accessdate=5 July 2020 |work=Radio Free Europe / Radio Liberty |date=19 November 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109105418/https://www.rferl.org/a/netherlands-propose-new-eu-human-rights-sanctions-regime/29609488.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>欧洲议会于2019年3月14日通过一项决议，呼吁理事会迅速建立欧盟一级的人权制裁机制。

2019年12月9日，[[欧盟外交和安全政策高级代表|欧盟外交和安全政策高级代表]][[何塞·博雷利·丰特列斯|何塞·博雷利·丰特列斯]]确认欧盟各国已达成强烈共识，因此[[歐洲對外事務部|歐洲對外事務部]]开始准备制裁制度的文件。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Barigazzi |first1=Jacopo |title=EU to prepare Magnitsky-style human rights sanctions regime |url=https://www.politico.eu/article/eu-to-prepare-magnitsky-style-human-rights-sanctions-regime/ |accessdate=5 July 2020 |work=Politico |date=9 December 2019 |archive-date=2020-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218130805/https://www.politico.eu/article/eu-to-prepare-magnitsky-style-human-rights-sanctions-regime/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>

欧洲议会于2020年6月15日通过一项关于[[香港国安法|香港国安法]]的决议，呼吁[[欧盟理事会|欧盟理事会]]完成制裁制度的筹备工作，以便利用该制度对负责香港国安立法的中国官员实施制裁。<ref>{{cite web |title=European Parliament resolution on the PRC national security law for Hong Kong and the need for the EU to defend Hong Kong's high degree of autonomy |url=https://www.europarl.europa.eu/doceo/document/RC-9-2020-0169_EN.html |website=European Parliament |accessdate=5 July 2020 |archive-date=2020-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200616154842/https://www.europarl.europa.eu/doceo/document/RC-9-2020-0169_EN.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

